Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:20.48,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}miwatasu kagiri ni hirogaru shikisai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:26.15,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}natsukashii bamen hodoite koboshita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:31.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}eranda ketsui wo shimetsukeru paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:37.16,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}todokanai asu ni shizumeta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:43.46,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}nigirishimeru kono te wo hirakeba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:51.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}furete shimau tou ni nageta kibou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:57.64,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}namida wo karashi mukau kono yami wo nuke
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:03.77,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}tsutsuganai mirai anata ga mitsumeteitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:09.11,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}yatto yatto tsukami kaketa hikari
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:13.07,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}daremo nanimo iwanakute ii
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:24.50,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}subete no kotae wa koko ni chanto aru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:20.48,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}As cores se espalham até onde o olhar alcança,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:26.15,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}uma cena nostálgica se desenrola e se espalham.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:31.61,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Um paradoxo que confunde nossas decisões,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:37.16,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}afundado em um amanhã inalcançável.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:43.46,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Se eu abrir essa mão que seguro com força,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:51.55,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}poderei alcançar a esperança que abandonei há muito tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:57.64,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Enxugue suas lágrimas e siga em frente para romper esta escuridão.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:03.77,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Mesmo quando você olha para um futuro sem esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:09.11,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Eu finalmente, finalmente, comecei a entender a luz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:13.07,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Não é preciso dizer nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:24.50,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Porque todas as respostas estão bem aqui.
